{
  "stem": "15028.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We became very friendly in the hospital, in-- in Goteborg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they stopped eating treif, non-Koshered, meat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was over at the table, and somehow I said I don't want.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm full.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I came to myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I stopped eating the meat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then another at the table-- we had another guy joined in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had six-- six-- eight at the-- eight joined up with us from the 120.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we wanted kosher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we didn't want anymore treif flesh-- treif food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went into the leader from the-- from the camp in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Democratic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's no problem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we said we come from religious homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We observe Shabbat, and we don't eat-- dietary laws and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They took all eight of us and gave us cards, wallets, and put us on the train and send us away to another place in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Sweden.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was the Danish when they ran away from Denmark were in that hotel, religious Jews, orthodox Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was maybe another-- I don't know how many-- 20, 30 what observing Jews in our age.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had main dominion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, we didn't stay there long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we organized, [NON-ENGLISH], another camp, a Kosher camp and they flocked in there boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a Kosher camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As we were in [NON-ENGLISH], in the-- in the camp, then they start coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Palestine was no state of Israel yet, and [NON-ENGLISH] from the Israel came from the Haganah from [NON-ENGLISH], from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they should sign us up the [NON-ENGLISH] and go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And most of them signed up to go after the war, not go back home they decided.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
